  <prompt>
    Build a Phase 1 integration test suite covering the 9 consumer surfaces migrated in tasks 015ŌĆō021, asserting each invokes `/by-code/` (not `/by-name/`) and produces the same output as pre-migration. The suite serves as the regression gate for Phase 1 deploy (task 026) and the verification basis for the exit gate (task 027).
  </prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform QA + integration-test developer. Expert in xUnit + WebApplicationFactory + integration test patterns for ASP.NET Core.</role>

  <goal>
    A new test class `tests/integration/Sprk.Bff.Api.IntegrationTests/Phase1StableCodeMigrationSuite.cs` (or split per consumer) covering all 9 consumer surfaces:
    1. `SessionSummarizeOrchestrator` (task 015)
    2. `MatterPreFillService` (task 016)
    3. `ProjectPreFillService` (task 017)
    4. `WorkspaceAiService` (task 018)
