    8. `ChatContextMappingService` (task 020)
    9. Frontend Pattern B sites (via E2E or mock ŌĆö `useAiSummary.ts`, `DocumentEmailWizard.tsx`) (task 021)
    Each test asserts the consumer uses `/by-code/`, returns expected output shape, AND `/by-name/` invocation count for that consumer is zero post-migration.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per spec ┬¦1.7 Test Strategy + FR-02 + FR-03 acceptance. The pre/post test pattern validates that migration preserved behavior. Each consumer surface gets ONE test asserting code-based resolution + output equivalence. Frontend surfaces are tested via either E2E (Playwright) or by mocking the API and asserting the call URL.
    </background>
