  <steps>
    <step order="1">Inspect the existing `tests/integration/Sprk.Bff.Api.IntegrationTests/` folder for shared fixture / WebApplicationFactory patterns.</step>
    <step order="2">Create `Phase1StableCodeMigrationSuite.cs` (or per-consumer files) with one Fact per consumer surface.</step>
    <step order="3">For each backend consumer (8 surfaces): seed a mock `IPlaybookLookupService` returning a typed playbook entity; invoke the consumer; assert (a) the call went through `GetByCodeAsync` (verify via Moq Verify or test-double counter), (b) output shape matches pre-migration contract.</step>
    <step order="4">For each frontend consumer (2 surfaces): either (a) write a Vitest test mocking fetch + asserting `/by-code/` URL pattern in the request; OR (b) document a manual smoke-test in `notes/handoffs/025-frontend-smoke-procedure.md`.</step>
    <step order="5">Add a cross-cutting test asserting `/by-name/` invocation count is zero across the test run for the migrated consumers (use a counting decorator over `IPlaybookLookupService` mocking the by-name path).</step>
    <step order="6">Run `dotnet test tests/integration/Sprk.Bff.Api.IntegrationTests/`. All 9 tests pass.</step>
    <step order="7">Run frontend tests (`npm run test`) for Vitest assertions if added.</step>
    <step order="8">Measure BFF publish size (test artifacts NOT included); report delta.</step>
    <step order="9">Update TASK-INDEX.md: task 025 ŌåÆ Ō£ģ.</step>
  </steps>

